Package com.fortify.pub.bugtracker.support

Class BugParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fortify.pub.bugtracker.support.BugParam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BugParamChoice, BugParamText, BugParamTextArea
    public abstract class BugParam
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
    A value object that represents a bug parameter that user needs to supply a value for at the time of filing the bug. A list of objects of this type are obtained from the bug tracker plugin to get information on the required bug parameters for this plugin
    See Also:
